Class ProteinSearch

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ProteinSearch
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    ProteinSearch Panel search proteins information in the DB Seacrh by protein index or protein Id (by astral id) If the server in down - an error dialog will apear If the searching parameters are incorrect- an error label will apear If the protein has a known structure- it's strucutre will open in RasMol (Must download the pdb~style DB before)
    Author:
    Litaf
